query:
/*+ NoMergeJoin(a1 q1 s t1 tq1 u1) */ select t1.name,
count(*)
from site AS s
inner join tag AS t1
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('chemistry',
'money',
'sharepoint',
'wordpress') AND t1.name IN ('client-object-model',
'custom-taxonomy',
'equilibrium',
'filters',
'images',
'mortgage',
'redox',
'theme-development',
'united-kingdom')
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id
inner join answer AS a1
on s.site_id = a1.site_id
inner join question AS q1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND a1.question_id = q1.id AND s.site_id = q1.site_id AND q1.score >= 1 AND q1.score <= 10
inner join so_user AS u1
on q1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND s.site_id = u1.site_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND u1.reputation >= 10 AND u1.reputation <= 100000 group by t1.name;
